  "content": {
    "prompt": "Napisati program koji iz datog stringa bri\u0161e sve samoglasnike.",
    "source_code": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nint main() {\n    char tekst[] = \"Ovo je neki primjer\";\n    char *s = tekst;\n    char *pocetak;\n\n    while (*s != '\\0') {\n        if (*s == 'a' || *s == 'e' || *s == 'i' || *s == 'o' || *s == 'u' ||\n            *s == 'A' || *s == 'E' || *s == 'I' || *s == 'O' || *s == 'U') {\n            pocetak = s;\n            while (*pocetak != '\\0') {\n                *pocetak = *(pocetak + 1);\n                pocetak++;\n            }\n        } else {\n            s++;\n        }\n    }\n\n    printf(\"%s\\n\", tekst);\n    return 0;\n}\n"
  },
